(9, 0, 'WP2', '1.8', 'to consider, on the basis of ITU R studies in accordance with Resolution 171 (WRC-19), appropriate regulatory actions, with a view to reviewing and, if necessary, revising Resolution 155 (Rev.WRC-19) and No. 5.484B to accommodate the use of fixed-satellite service (FSS) networks by control and non-payload communications of unmanned aircraft systems;', 'APG23-4/INP-24(Rev.1)', 'Iran (Islamic Republic of)', 'Arasteh: Method A (no Change) is not a viable option:\nInterference management belym didefinisikan dengan baik, banyak ambiguitas yang muncul pada resolusi saat ini. Terdapat 8 stake holder yang terkait mengenai isu agenda item ini', '', 'Harfan Hian Ryanu', '2022-08-16 08:40:36'),
(10, 0, 'WP2', '1.8', 'to consider, on the basis of ITU R studies in accordance with Resolution 171 (WRC-19), appropriate regulatory actions, with a view to reviewing and, if necessary, revising Resolution 155 (Rev.WRC-19) and No. 5.484B to accommodate the use of fixed-satellite service (FSS) networks by control and non-payload communications of unmanned aircraft systems;', 'APG23-4/INP-35', 'Iran (Islamic Republic of)', 'Arasteh: Method B merupakan pekerjaan yang belum selesai,  terdapat disclaimer pada draft CPM untuk method B, tidak ada regulatory procedure untuk Method B, sehingga method B saat ini masih invalid statusnya\r\nPer Hovstad (Chair ITU-R WP5B) mengatakan apabila sudah selesai kajiannya, method B akan terdiri dari beberapa approach (B1, B2, B3)', '', 'Harfan Hian Ryanu', '2022-08-16 08:45:24'),
(11, 0, 'WP2', '1.8', 'to consider, on the basis of ITU R studies in accordance with Resolution 171 (WRC-19), appropriate regulatory actions, with a view to reviewing and, if necessary, revising Resolution 155 (Rev.WRC-19) and No. 5.484B to accommodate the use of fixed-satellite service (FSS) networks by control and non-payload communications of unmanned aircraft systems;', 'APG23-4/INP-75', 'Iran (Islamic Republic of)', 'Arasteh:  tidak ada regulatory procedure untuk Method B, sehingga method B saat ini masih invalid statusnya', '', 'Harfan Hian Ryanu', '2022-08-16 09:04:20'),
(12, 0, 'WP2', '1.8', 'to consider, on the basis of ITU R studies in accordance with Resolution 171 (WRC-19), appropriate regulatory actions, with a view to reviewing and, if necessary, revising Resolution 155 (Rev.WRC-19) and No. 5.484B to accommodate the use of fixed-satellite service (FSS) networks by control and non-payload communications of unmanned aircraft systems;', 'APG23-4/INF-25', 'Iran (Islamic Republic of)', 'Arastee: the draft CPM text is unfinished as stated in disclaimer, method B is proposed to be deleted.', 'ASDASJDSAJD', 'Harfan Hian Ryanu', '2022-08-16 09:12:40'),
(13, 0, 'WP1', '1.1', 'to consider, based on the results of the ITU R studies, possible measures to address, in the frequency band 4 800-4 990 MHz, protection of stations of the aeronautical and maritime mobile services located in international airspace and waters from other stations located within national territories, and to review the pfd criteria in No. 5.441B in accordance with Resolution 223 (Rev.WRC-19);', 'APG23-4/INP-07', 'Australia', 'Menolak karena ....', '', 'Gelar Budiman', '2022-09-05 06:27:09');
